  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(54, 54, 165);">Welcome to "Give and Take for FREE", a smart process to reuse our household things.</p>
  <br>
  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(54, 54, 165);">Give - In today's age, we human invent new things everyday to make our life comfortable. We prioritize the new items over the backdated one, also our requirement changes everyday. So when we stop using some item, some people give the item to others which is good but some dump it into the trash. In this web application you can share the informaton about your item which you want to donate.</p>
  <br>   
  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(54, 54, 165);">Take - On the other hand, if you need something you can use this application to search the item you are looking for. If it is available, you can simply contact the giver and pick the item from the giver.</p>
  <br>   
  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(54, 54, 165);">It is a free service and our intention is just to reuse things until their value ends. Our intention is not to involve any kind of monetory transactions.</p>

